Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.49,0:00:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間的黃昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.73,0:00:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行著一段永遠的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.64,0:00:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖繼續探索著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.05,0:01:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片發出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.02,0:01:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺失的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.74,0:01:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手的掌心確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.08,0:01:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.38,0:01:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間開始流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 還沒到會面時間唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情已經不用擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好去上學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是畢業典禮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.33,0:02:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…\N已經到了這種季節了呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟祐一有好好相處嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…有啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.24,0:02:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由從我的面前消失之後\N已經過了一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生意外的秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在則在做復健逐漸復原當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.32,0:02:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那天以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和名雪之間就若有似無的\N互相避開對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季節 走到了春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「風所到達的地方」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很適合妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.39,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 全身上下都散發出\N高雅文靜的淑女氣質呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.90,0:03:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是跟某個粗暴的人\N完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.83,0:03:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N真的是人要衣裝啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 說的太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有別的話可以說了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞在不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛\N要變矮了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們兩個決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的學校雖然畢業很難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要進去\N卻是非常的簡單哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…就算是再怎麼簡單也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.38,0:04:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟小舞在一起的話 對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是要道別了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是就不能見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.96,0:04:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤同學可真的是\N不能疏忽大意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞 妳的身體沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 托你的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是什麼都沒有做喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.38,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 都是多虧了祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然姊姊也有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 那種講法\N好像順便的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.43,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 春天開始\N就可以跟大家一起上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為出席數不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要重讀一年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.54,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種身高就算說是一年級\N也不會有人奇怪的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭說那種話的人了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次跟我一起做雪人好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.56,0:05:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做一個最大的\N作為我恢復健康的紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是40公尺高之類的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼肯定啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我從小就有的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.43,0:05:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一個人是沒辦法做\N那麼大的雪人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,40公尺是不可能的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在也已經沒有積雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以等到下一個冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意跟我一起做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 事實上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.72,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮羅幾時回來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從醫院回來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠就在門口等著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.47,0:06:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 這些日子\N到底是跑到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真會讓人操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是真是太好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣一來\N就算祐一會不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也比較不會那麼寂寞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.89,0:06:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨發生了意外對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像因為那樣\N我老媽就覺得很擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.93,0:06:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說還是要住在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要搬去的地點也確定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪她知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤同學要轉學這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒跟她講嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有跟她提過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.18,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易終於可以跟祐一\N一起上同樣的學校了說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別露出那種表情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.65,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放假的時候\N我還會再到這裡來玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺會有點寂寞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經…整理的差不多了呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該送的東西都送光了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.13,0:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.07,0:07:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車票也弄好了\N後天三點的特快車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉學好像要辦很多手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很麻煩\N但是在春假結束前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.38,0:07:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去醫院了\N晚餐你自己先吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一說 後天就要回家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說車票也已經買好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一個人沒問題嗎…？ 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有祐一叫我起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以自己起床的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那個意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.78,0:08:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳小的時候 可是哭的很厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.05,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳呀 一直哭著說\N叫祐一不要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是幾歲的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4、5歲的時候吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.63,0:08:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候祐一明明說\N放假的時候會再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是名雪卻還是一直哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣子嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對自己誠實一點吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.24,0:09:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再勉強忍耐\N把自己的心意全部說出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果對象是祐一的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有什麼不好意思的\N不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安！祐一！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由…妳為什麼會在這裡…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.57,0:09:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正要做餅乾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.67,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餅乾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我還想要把它送給祐一呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.61,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦 一定又會燒焦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.35,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有認真的\N跟秋子阿姨學了做法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不過學了一下下\N手藝就會變好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也煮粥煮成功了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.73,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨也說很好吃\N把粥吃掉了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種話一聽就知道是客套話了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好了\N如果看起來好吃的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我吃也是可以的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.77,0:10:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要命 睡太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.23,0:10:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北川…還有香里跟栞也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我叫他們來的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是祐一的餞行會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.81,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要搬走了\N怎麼不早點跟我說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易跟你成為朋友的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會寂寞的耶~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦！北川\N我忘記跟你說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個好好吃~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是栞親手做的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個對吧 親手做的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快拿出來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.57,0:11:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手制的圍巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花都已經開了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季節完全不合…對吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我會珍惜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明很高興的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…為什麼眼淚會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻瓜呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美阪 我也好想要喔\N手制圍巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己編吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡咖啡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N主角坐好就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 相澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會再見面的對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳們 香里 栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北川也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無誠意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.90,0:12:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多保重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該整理整理了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.54,0:12:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.01,0:12:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為祐一的眼裡\N總是只有亞由一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家裡我來整理就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先去醫院好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想媽媽她在等你吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪在躲著我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 在躲避的人是我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到在兩人之間的氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟是這麼的凝重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.81,0:13:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果 我仍然只是\N一直在傷害名雪吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…必須要道歉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.72,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前 我把名雪送我的雪兔\N弄壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又糟蹋了她的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪她不論過了多久\N都還只是個孩子呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是那種到了現在都還深信著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.23,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有白馬王子來迎接她的類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.17,0:13:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 戀愛\N是為了讓人成長而存在的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.91,0:13:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使那份思念沒有實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也會累積於生命之中\N不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使那份思念沒有實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也會累積於生命之中\N不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累積於生命之中嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不送我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 今天媽媽要做檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…替我向秋子阿姨問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.71,0:14:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.78,0:14:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去給祐一送行好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 這樣就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也差不多該走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.63,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這鬧鐘還沒有當面還給名雪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？想吃東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要生氣聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.85,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 即使到現在\N都還是最喜歡祐一的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從七年前就一直一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒關係了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使祐一不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒有關係哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.55,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 現在趕快到醫院去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊 電車已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有一個等著祐一的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.92,0:16:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從七年前開始一直等著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.13,0:16:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那樣…名雪 妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.84,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這是第一次\N也是最後一次了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你…快點去吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡流動的景色…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.61,0:17:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天 白雪飛舞的城鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一邊留下新的足跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊在商店街跑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天 積雪溶化的城鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡用手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.66,0:17:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將遺落在樹木下的小雪球\N撿起來的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天 忘卻雪的寒冷的城鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡從放在肩膀上的\N傘的縫隙中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.21,0:18:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,望著朦朧的街景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.78,0:18:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋天 訴說著\N冬天即將到來的城鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡用手去接住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.32,0:18:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個從仰望著的雲中\N落下的小小的雪的結晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後季節來到了冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.56,0:18:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮被雪白的顏色\N所覆蓋的季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.03,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡流動的季節…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.97,0:18:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…\N就像在雪中凍結住的水珠一般…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的時間也停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有季節分別的時間當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是只有一個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不停的重複…不停的重複…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.95,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在夢中一直看著相同的景色…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.29,0:18:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把自己托付在\N沒有黎明的夜裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚開始泛出了曙光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.35,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好慢 太慢了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那個帽子是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不會笑我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.23,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會笑妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會笑我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好歹我也是個信守約定的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種說法\N一點說服力都沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了理髮店剪頭髮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.44,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被剪掉了一大堆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你一定會笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛啊 看來像個小男生一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 我是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心的話\N就說聲「人家」來聽聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很壞心眼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實明明就很溫柔的 對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊 突然這樣講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在呼喚著我的名字吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽見祐一的聲音了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.72,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳等了七年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再到任何地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會一直待在妳身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.94,0:20:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以亞由\N請妳張開眼睛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都在叫我對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為祐一一直呼喚著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才醒過來的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫做奇跡對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能像這樣再和祐一見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約好了對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.14,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說過只要是我能做得到的\N都會幫妳實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要去吃鯛魚燒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣已經變暖和了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人在賣鯛魚燒了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心 因為有秋子阿姨會做嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鯛魚燒可以自己做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.52,0:21:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想做看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.92,0:21:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.89,0:21:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會做成變形鯛魚燒的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.29,0:21:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.56,0:21:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始練習的話就會做了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要到幾時才學得會呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 也好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.90,0:21:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們的時間多的是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞由 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.75,0:23:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪溶化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.69,0:23:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回憶的深處被雪白的雪的結晶\N完全的掩蓋住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.43,0:23:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 那個結晶\N和春天的陽光一起開始溶化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.03,0:23:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被冰凍住的時間\N開始緩緩的向前行進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.94,0:23:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡就在我們的心中
